<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. فِي الْعَجْزِ مَفْزَعُهُمْ إِلَى السُّلْطَانِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لا عُجْبَ إِذْ ضَلُّوا هِدَايَةَ دِينِهِمْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَنْ يَرْجِعُوا لِلْجَهْلِ وَالْعِصْيَانِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>هَا قَدْ غَلَوْا فِي الأَوْلِيَاءِ وَقُبُورُهُمْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَضْحَتْ يُحَجُّ لَهَا مِن الْبُلْدَانِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَبَنَوْا عَلَى تِلْكَ الْقُبُورِ مَسَاجِدًا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَالنَّصُّ جَاءَ لَهُمْ بِلَعْنِ الْبَانِي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَكَذَاكَ قَدْ صَنَعُوا لَهَا الأَقْفَاصَ تُو<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ضَعُ فَوْقَهَا فِي غَايَةِ الإِتْقَانِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>يَكْسُونَهَا بِمَطَارِفٍ مَنْقُوشَةٍ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>قَدْ كَلَّفَتْهُمْ بَاهِظَ الأَثْمَانِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بَلْ عِنْدَ رَأْسِ الْقَبْرِ تَلْقَى نُصْبَهُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>قَدْ عَمَّمُوهَا عِمَّةَ الشَّيْخَانِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَلَسَوْفَ إِنْ طَالَ الزَّمَانُ بِهِمْ تَرَى<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَلَهَا يَدَانِ تَلِيهِمَا الرِّجْلانِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَدَعَوْهُمُوا شُفَعَاءَهُمْ أَيْضًا كَمَا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>قَدْ كَانَ يَزْعُمُ عَابِدُو الأَوْثَانِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَتَقَرَّبُوا لَهُمُوا بِتَسْيِيبِ السِّوَا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>ثِبِ وَالنُّذُورِ وَسَائِرِ الْقُرْبَانِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَتَمَسَّحُوا بِقُبُورِهِمْ وَسُتُورِهِمْ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَكَذَاكَ بِالأَقْفَاصِ وَالْجُدْرَانِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>